<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <title>Home Page</title>

  <meta charset="UTF-8" >
  <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" >
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" >

  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/vendor/normalize-4.1.1.css" />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/vendor/border-box.css" />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/main.css" />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/layout.css" />

  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Gabarito:wght@400;500;600&family=Young+Serif&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

  <script src="/vendor/jquery-3.0.0.js"></script>
  <script defer src="/scripts/app.js"></script>

  <!-- Font Awesome -->
  <script src="https://kit.fontawesome.com/21c6db8c84.js" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</head>
<body>
  <%- include('partials/nav') %>
  <header>
    <h1>Hire expert Programmers for any job</h1>
    <img src="../images/home.png" alt="image of woman on computer">
  </header>
  <main>
    <div id="top-row">
      <div class="feature">
        <span class="profile-container">
          <img src="../images/female-1.png" alt="profile image">
        </span>
        <p>Unlock the potential of your projects by hiring me, a seasoned software developer. With my skills and experience, I'll ensure your software is robust, efficient, and tailored to your exact needs. </p>
        <a href="/listings/1" id="id-path">
          <button type="submit" class="hire-me">Hire Me!</button>
        </a>
      </div>
      <div class="feature">
        <span class="profile-container">
          <img src="../images/female-2.png" alt="profile image">
        </span>
        <p>Looking for a web development expert? Search no further! I specialize in creating stunning and functional websites that are not only visually appealing but also optimized for performance and user experience. </p>
        <a href="/listings/2" id="id-path">
          <button type="submit" class="hire-me">Hire Me!</button>
        </a>
      </div>
      <div class="feature">
        <span class="profile-container">
          <img src="../images/male-3.png" alt="profile image">
        </span>
        <p>Elevate your business with a mobile app developer who knows the ropes. I can turn your app ideas into reality, providing efficient, scalable, and secure solutions for both iOS and Android platforms. </p>
        <a href="/listings/3" id="id-path">
          <button type="submit" class="hire-me">Hire Me!</button>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div id="bottom-row">
      <div class="feature">
        <span class="profile-container">
          <img src="../images/male-2.png" alt="profile image">
        </span>
        <p>Data-driven decisions are the key to success. As a data science and analytics specialist, I can help you harness the power of data to make informed choices, optimize processes, and drive business growth. </p>
        <a href="/listings/4" id="id-path">
          <button type="submit" class="hire-me">Hire Me!</button>
        </a>
      </div>
      <div class="feature">
        <span class="profile-container">
          <img src="../images/female-4.png" alt="profile image">
        </span>
        <p>Protect your digital assets with my cybersecurity expertise. I specialize in fortifying your systems, applications, and data from cyber threats, ensuring your business stays secure and compliant. </p>
        <a href="/listings/5" id="id-path">
          <button type="submit" class="hire-me">Hire Me!</button>
        </a>
      </div>
      <div class="feature">
        <span class="profile-container">
          <img src="../images/male-1.png" alt="profile image">
        </span>
        <p>Explore the possibilities of AI and machine learning with me. I'm passionate about applying cutting-edge technologies to solve complex problems and drive innovation in your projects. </p>
        <a href="/listings/6" id="id-path">
          <button type="submit" class="hire-me">Hire Me!</button>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <a href="/listings" id="listings-bottom">
      <button type="submit" id="listings-button">Find your programmer today!</button>
    </a>
  </main>
  <%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>
